    "description": "你的太阳核心正受到外星人入侵的威胁。你有能力保护核心并拯救世界吗？<br><br>选择一艘拥有独特能力和武器的飞船，抵御入侵的外星人。面对一波波愈发强大的外星飞船。为了生存，你必须不断调整并升级你的飞船和太阳核心。找到并摧毁外星母舰，减缓入侵速度，增加生存机会。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113390/extras/30014054560f120c7d3ec1839b3668ef.poster.avif?t=1737576410\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113390/extras/30014054560f120c7d3ec1839b3668ef.webm?t=1737576410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113390/extras/30014054560f120c7d3ec1839b3668ef.mp4?t=1737576410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>发现超过60种不同的升级选项，强化你的飞船。明智地选择，创造强大的组合来击退入侵者的攻击。每一轮都有新的机会发现协同效应。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113390/extras/5a9d551690ceb19171cd843e2587cb2b.poster.avif?t=1737576410\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113390/extras/5a9d551690ceb19171cd843e2587cb2b.webm?t=1737576410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113390/extras/5a9d551690ceb19171cd843e2587cb2b.mp4?t=1737576410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>升级你的核心以提升生存几率。激光、火箭和护盾可供你使用。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113390/extras/b82861265bc1e5a29bf8e698d64d9f68.poster.avif?t=1737576410\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113390/extras/b82861265bc1e5a29bf8e698d64d9f68.webm?t=1737576410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113390/extras/b82861265bc1e5a29bf8e698d64d9f68.mp4?t=1737576410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>对外星母舰发起反击，摧毁它们的生成点，减少核心的压力。小心，如果不及时攻击母舰，它们会越来越靠近。谨慎规划你的反击，因为此时你的核心将毫无防御。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113390/extras/a836064571df7b179374ccdaf1b4c210.poster.avif?t=1737576410\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113390/extras/a836064571df7b179374ccdaf1b4c210.webm?t=1737576410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113390/extras/a836064571df7b179374ccdaf1b4c210.mp4?t=1737576410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>主要特点： <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>选择一艘拥有独特武器和属性的飞船 []试玩版提供超过40种升级选择，允许无数种配置 <br></li><li>保护你的太阳核心，抵御持续30到90秒的波次进攻 <br></li><li>快速游戏回合（少于30分钟） <br></li><li>收集太空垃圾来购买新升级和修复核心 </li></ul>",
